    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Used to treat stomach ache, as an appetizer, an abortive, blood depurative, diabetes, tuberculosis, antihypertensive, antimalarial, applied to wounds, antipyretic.</td>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Aerial parts and leaves</td>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">[
